### launch a lmsh shell name like sh7t.py
```
~/.local/bin/terminal/wt  "C:\Program Files\Git\bin\bash.exe" -li -c "cd ~/echo-home/workstation/lmstudio/promptia/ && ./sh7t.py --port 8082"
```

### Notes
lmsh shell must be run under `wt` command above
